## Creating an encrypted container:
fallocate -l 4GB ~/.Qubes/mount/Archive
sudo cryptsetup -v luksFormat ~/.Qubes/mount/Archive
sudo cryptsetup -v luksOpen /home/sysadmin/.Qubes/mount/Archive Archive
sudo mkfs -t ext4 /dev/mapper/Archive

# Mounting an encrypted container an a VM:
## dom0:
sudo cryptsetup -v luksOpen /home/sysadmin/.Qubes/mount/Archive Archive
qvm-block | grep Archive
# <host>:<drive> Documents 3 GiB
qvm-block attach <vmname> <host>:<drive>
## VM:
mkdir ~/Archive
sudo mount /dev/xvdi ~/Archive
sudo chown user:user ~/Archive
